Ba musulmans baye babomaki pulusu lobi loleki, bakosambisama lelo na lombangu penza pe bakoki kokoto prison pe mokolo kaka mwa lelo.

Lobi loleki o engumba Kinshasa, nzinga nzinga ya palais du peuple na stades des martyrs, bitumba bizalaki makasi kati ya ba musulmans bakambami na makonzi babale. Na bitumba wana, batumbaki pulusu moko, 3 mituka ya ba pulusu pe babebisaki mituka 11 ya bato pe bayika kati na bango bazokaki pota inene.



Kasi ba pulusu bakangaki ba musulmans ebele, sima ye bitumba wana.  O kati ya bakangemi, ba oyo babomaki pulusu bazwami. 

Pona bosukisi sanza ya Ramadan, ba musulmans bayokanaki bakutana na stades des martyrs . Kasi yango elekaki ndenge bakanisaki te. Ba musulmans baye bakambami na Chek Abdallah Mangala na baye bakambami na Imam Youssouf.

 

 

Biche Mwangaz